The reason the meek do not rule is not because they havent in the past. Its simply because they are alwaays overthrown by angry masses when they proved inadequate leaders. <br>
<br>
All technology is a two edged sword. In the end risks must be taken to advaance the human race. Who takes those risks is dependant on whether those leading the way choose to procrastinate. Those who instead seek to open the door of knowledge can aaccomplish great things. The procrastinaators can look forward to seeing others eventually open the door and recieve the benefits.<br>
<br>
The worst possible scenario for fusion research is a better bomb. But who would you prefer in posesssssion of this technology. The US or another nation such as China. The correct decision for the US would be to pursue and discover the true potential of fusion technology. A difficult decision not for the meek. <br>
